OL,4,CAfghanistan: Pen Farthing sorry for
OL,5,Cfoul-mouthed message to aide
OL,6, A former Royal Marine said his emotions
OL,7, "got the better" of him when he left an
OL,8, expletive-laden message for a
OL,9, government aide as he tried to get his
OL,10, staff and animals out of Afghanistan.
OL,12,FPaul "Pen" Farthing arrived in the UK
OL,13,Fon a private charter flight on Sunday
OL,14,Fwith some 150 animals from his rescue
OL,15,Fshelter in Kabul.
OL,17,FHe said he had spent weeks campaigning
OL,18,Fto get his employees and animals out.
OL,20,F"I was at the lowest point I could
OL,21,Fpossibly be," he said.
